==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: landing gear
<hw>land"ing gear`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The wheels and attached
structures under an airplane that support it and allow it to move when
on the ground; also, the floats or pontoons of an amphibious airplane
together with their supporting structures. Landing gear may be fixed
rigidly in place, or retractable when in flight.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>landing strip</ent>⟦br⟧
